# Code of Conduct

## Purpose
To foster a welcoming, inclusive, and respectful environment for all participants.

## Expected Behavior
- Be respectful and considerate to others.
- Communicate openly and thoughtfully.
- Accept constructive criticism gracefully.
- Respect differing viewpoints and experiences.

## Unacceptable Behavior
- Harassment, discrimination, or exclusion of any kind.
- Offensive or inappropriate language or imagery.
- Personal attacks or insults.
- Disruptive or disrespectful conduct.

## Reporting Issues
If you experience or witness unacceptable behavior, please report it to the project maintainers at [contact email or method].

## Enforcement
Violations may result in warnings, temporary bans, or permanent removal from the project.

---

*This Code of Conduct is adapted from the Contributor Covenant (https://www.contributor-covenant.org/).*